		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">翠翎恐蕈进行左划、啄地、起跳至多三段的普通攻击，起跳<span color="#bfffbf">自身附着草</span><span>，左划与啄地造成</span><span color="#99ff86">60%</span><span>伤害，起跳造成</span><span color="#99ff86">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="437" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">翠翎恐蕈进行左扫、右扫、翻扫至多三段的攻击。每一扫都扔出5个孢弹，且均<span color="#bfffbf">自身附着草</span><span>，每个孢弹造成</span><span color="#99ff87">30%,15%,<br/>3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">翠翎恐蕈产生菌雾，向空中吟叫3次后产生爆炸<span color="#bfffbf">(前2次自身挂草)</span><span>，造成</span><span color="#99ff87">50%</span><span>伤害，并向外产生2道扩散震波，也造成</span><span color="#99ff87">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="439" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当翠翎恐蕈自身被触发燃烧时，其会变黑，然后发射3个大型孢子，只能使用<span color="#ff9999">火</span><span>和</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>摧毁，每个孢子爆炸造成</span><span color="#99ff86">50%</span><span>伤害，并召唤1个枯焦的浮游草蕈兽，之后翠翎恐蕈恢复正常。场上至多存在4个召唤的蕈兽。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1072" width="425" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">怒气：<span color="#99ff86">100草</span><span>充能盾，受到雷元素攻击</span><span color="#99ff86">+2</span><span>/次，触发任意激化</span><span color="#99ff86">+15</span><span>/次，受到火元素攻击</span><span color="#99ff86">-34</span><span>/次。触发燃烧直接枯焦。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/翠翎恐蕈.assets/Image_14.png')" x="720" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/翠翎恐蕈.assets/Image_15.png')" x="720" y="361">
		</BitmapImage>
